Package: DECODE
Type: Package
Title: Deciphering Cancer Origin from DNA Evolution
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Khanh N.", "Dinh", email = "dinhngockhanh@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Decomposes genomic variants from bulk DNA-sequencing into a neutral tail
    and mutation clusters based on their Variant Allele Frequencies (VAFs), with
    corrections for sample-specific DNA-sequencing coverage distribution and mutation
    calling biases in the Site Frequency Spectrum (SFS).
